title: Ai Zhi Su Vegetarian
description: Love Su-vegetarian restaurant. Philosophy: the promotion of vegetarianism, with love to serve the public, to bring convenience to vegetarians, at the same time to save our planet. Owner and employees are vegetarians.  No eggs, no alcohol, no smoking. Offering a variety of specialties throughout the year. Chinese Name: 爱之素素食餐厅 Chinese Address: 漳州市水仙大街新元城市花园5C幢1号店面.
